    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Enthralled by Song</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Dr George F Gitlitz letter comments on May 16 article on bird song</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In '' 'Revolutionary Etude,' Rendered by a Wren'' (May 16), I was struck by the question, ''Are there cases when humans, like certain birds, have a sexual response to songs?'' A year ago, we heard Frankie Avalon sing; when he finished, women in the audience went nuts. I said to my wife, ''They're giving him a standing ovulation!''</p>
        <p>DR . GEORGE  F. GITLITZ  Sarasota, Fla.</p>
      </block>
